metadata.name: The Embryo
metadata.description:
This is first NFT in a collection of 4 photographs that have been issued as a single, unique edition.

5000  x  8897 px

The fusion of one form into another, simplicity and at the same time uniqueness.

Now I am not ashamed to talk about it and show it so intimately.



It's more than art.

It's depth, it's natural.
